OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeriod pants could get     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcheaper after tax lifted   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Period underwear could be set to fall  
OL,6, in price after the government said the 
OL,7, product would no longer be subject to  
OL,8, value added tax (VAT) from 1 January.  
OL,10,FRemoving the tax should make the pants,
OL,11,Fseen as a greener alternative to       
OL,12,Ftampons and sanitary towels, up to #2  
OL,13,Fcheaper per pair, the Treasury said.   
OL,15,FThe move follows a campaign by         
OL,16,Fretailers and charities for the tax to 
OL,17,Fbe lifted.                             
OL,19,FOther period products such as tampons  
OL,20,Fand pads have been exempt since 2021.  
